title: Always Has - The Yak's Best Moments: Part II
description:
Some of our favorite bits such as: the first time we heard about Nick's straight dad along with his first pick in fantasy football this year, how Barron Trump became a running gag, a throwback to our discussion about feral hogs, the origin of Libs from the Sticks, Owen goes undercover and asks Dave to lunch along with Owen's bugged review with Gaz, creating the Rasslin' theme song, F*ck FM's debut, Chad Kroeger singing Rockstar, a throwback to the Enterprise Rent-A-Car phone call, and KB's creepy New Year's facebook message from his orthodontist!!!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolyak
